<L>__{exterior tatooine rock mesa dune sea coastline day}
<A>__{from high on a rock mesa, the tiny landspeeder can be seen gliding across the desert floor. suddenly in the foreground two weather beaten sandpeople shrouded in their grimy desert cloaks peer over the edge of the rock mesa. one of the marginally human creatures raises a long ominous laser rifle and points it at the speeder but the second creature grabs the gun before it can be fired. the sandpeople, or tusken raiders as they're sometimes called, speak in a coarse barbaric language as they get into an animated argument. the second tusken raider seems to get in the final word and the nomads scurry over the rocky terrain.}
